TY  - JOUR
TI  - Turnover Liquidity and the Transmission of Monetary Policy
AU  - Lagos, Ricardo
AU  - Zhang, Shengxing
AB  - [We provide empirical evidence of a novel liquidity-based transmission mechanism through which monetary policy influences asset markets, develop a model of this mechanism, and assess the ability of the quantitative theory to match the evidence.]
